reviewText: It is very enjoyable with a lot of clever dialogue.  The acting is great and the messages are conveyed in a thoughtful, warm, and compassionate way.  They successfully meshed the 70's atmosphere of small film production with current sensibilities.  This movie reminds us to all have a sense of humor about the human condition, and see the irony in many things we do in life.
